    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
